# Privacy Policy for Krishi Mitra Price

**Last updated:** 1st Jan 2025

## Introduction

Krishi Mitra Price ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application (the "App").

Please read this privacy policy carefully. If you do not agree with the terms of this privacy policy, please do not access the application.

---

## Information We Collect

### 1. Personal Information

When you register for an account, we may collect:

- **Email address** (via Google Sign-In)
- **Name and profile picture** (via Google Sign-In)
- **Google account ID** (for authentication purposes)

### 2. Location Information

To provide personalized services, we collect:

- **Approximate location** (city/district level)
- **GPS coordinates** (only when you use location-based features)

**Purpose:**
- Display weather information for your area
- Show relevant local market (mandi) prices
- Provide location-specific price predictions

**Note:** We do NOT track your real-time location or share it with third parties.

### 3. Device Information

We automatically collect:

- Device model and manufacturer
- Operating system version
- Unique device identifiers
- App version
- Device language settings

### 4. Usage Information

We collect information about how you use the app:

- Features you access
- Screens you view
- Time spent on the app
- Commodities you search for
- Analysis types you use
- App crashes and errors

---

## How We Use Your Information

We use the collected information for:

### 1. Providing Core Services
- Authenticate your account via Google Sign-In
- Generate personalized price predictions
- Display local weather forecasts
- Show relevant market prices

### 2. Improving User Experience
- Remember your preferences (language, favorite commodities)
- Improve app performance and stability
- Fix bugs and technical issues
- Develop new features based on usage patterns

### 3. Analytics & Research
- Understand how users interact with the app
- Measure app performance
- Generate aggregate statistics (no individual identification)

### 4. Communication
- Send important app updates (rare)
- Respond to your support requests
- Notify you of new features (optional, can opt-out)

---

## How We Share Your Information

### We DO NOT Sell Your Data

We will never sell, rent, or lease your personal information to third parties.

### Third-Party Service Providers

We share data only with trusted service providers:

#### 1. Google Sign-In (Authentication)
- **What we share:** Google account ID (automatically handled)
- **Purpose:** User authentication
- **Privacy Policy:** https://policies.google.com/privacy

#### 2. Firebase Analytics (Google)
- **What we share:** Usage data, device info (anonymized)
- **Purpose:** App analytics and performance monitoring
- **Privacy Policy:** https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy

#### 3. Google AdMob (Advertising)
- **What we share:** Device ID, ad interaction data
- **Purpose:** Display relevant advertisements
- **Privacy Policy:** https://policies.google.com/privacy
- **Note:** You can limit ad personalization in device settings

#### 4. Government Data Sources
- **What we collect FROM them:** Public market prices from AGMARKNET
- **What we share WITH them:** Nothing (read-only access)

### Legal Requirements

We may disclose your information if required by law or in response to valid legal requests.

---

## Data Security

### Security Measures

We implement industry-standard security measures:

- **Encryption in Transit:** All data transmitted using HTTPS/TLS
- **Secure Authentication:** Google OAuth 2.0 protocol
- **Access Controls:** Limited employee access to user data
- **Regular Security Audits:** Continuous monitoring for vulnerabilities

### Data Retention

- **Account Data:** Retained until you delete your account
- **Usage Analytics:** Aggregated data retained indefinitely (anonymized)
- **Logs:** Error logs retained for 90 days

### Important Note

While we use reasonable security measures, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.

---

## Your Privacy Rights

### You Have the Right To:

#### 1. Access Your Data
Request a copy of personal data we hold about you.

#### 2. Correct Your Data
Update inaccurate or incomplete information.

#### 3. Delete Your Data
Request deletion of your account and associated data.

**How to delete your account:**
- Option 1: Go to Settings ‚Üí Account ‚Üí Delete Account
- Option 2: Email us at: support@genhybrid.in
- Option 3: Uninstall the app (deletes local data)

#### 4. Opt-Out of Analytics
You can disable analytics in Settings ‚Üí Privacy ‚Üí Analytics

#### 5. Limit Ad Personalization
- Android: Settings ‚Üí Google ‚Üí Ads ‚Üí Opt out of Ads Personalization
- Or in our app: Settings ‚Üí Privacy ‚Üí Limit Ads

#### 6. Export Your Data
Request a downloadable copy of your data (CSV/JSON format).

---

## Data We Do NOT Collect

For your peace of mind, we explicitly DO NOT collect:

- ‚ùå Financial information (bank accounts, credit cards)
- ‚ùå Sensitive personal data (religion, caste, political views)
- ‚ùå Real-time location tracking
- ‚ùå Contacts from your device
- ‚ùå SMS or call logs
- ‚ùå Photos or files from your device
- ‚ùå Microphone or camera access (unless you explicitly grant for specific features)

---

## Children's Privacy

Our app is not intended for children under 13 years of age.

We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us at support@genhybrid.in, and we will delete it immediately.

---

## Location Services

### How We Use Location

- **Approximate Location:** Used to show local weather and nearby market prices
- **Precise Location:** Only used if you manually enter location or enable GPS for weather
- **Frequency:** Only when you open relevant screens (weather, market selection)

### How to Control Location Access

- **Android:** Settings ‚Üí Apps ‚Üí Krishi Mitra ‚Üí Permissions ‚Üí Location
- Options: Allow all the time / Allow only while using / Deny

### No Location Sharing

We do NOT:
- Share your location with other users
- Track your movements
- Store historical location data
- Use location for marketing purposes

---

## Cookies and Tracking Technologies

### What We Use

- **Session Tokens:** To keep you logged in
- **Preferences:** To remember your language and settings
- **Analytics SDKs:** Firebase Analytics (can be disabled)
- **Ad SDKs:** Google AdMob (uses advertising ID)

### How to Control

- Disable analytics: Settings ‚Üí Privacy ‚Üí Analytics
- Reset advertising ID: Device Settings ‚Üí Google ‚Üí Ads

---

## Third-Party Links

Our app may contain links to third-party websites or services:

- Government AGMARKNET website
- Weather service providers
- Agricultural news sources

**Important:** We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third-party sites. Please review their privacy policies.

---

## International Data Transfers

Our app primarily serves users in India. However, some service providers (Google/Firebase) may process data in:

- United States
- European Union
- Other countries where Google operates data centers

All international transfers comply with applicable data protection laws.

---

## California Privacy Rights (CCPA)

If you are a California resident, you have additional rights:

- Right to know what data we collect
- Right to delete your data
- Right to opt-out of sale (Note: We don't sell data)
- Right to non-discrimination

To exercise these rights, email: support@genhybrid.in

---

## European Privacy Rights (GDPR)

If you are in the European Union, you have rights under GDPR:

- Right to access
- Right to rectification
- Right to erasure
- Right to restrict processing
- Right to data portability
- Right to object
- Right to withdraw consent

**Our Legal Basis for Processing:**
- **Consent:** For analytics and personalized ads
- **Contract:** To provide app services you've requested
- **Legitimate Interest:** To improve app performance

To exercise GDPR rights, email: support@genhybrid.in

---

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be effective when:

1. We post the updated policy in the app
2. We update the "Last updated" date
3. For material changes: We'll notify you via app notification or email

**Your continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance.**

We encourage you to review this policy periodically.

---

## Data Breach Notification

In the unlikely event of a data breach affecting your personal information:

1. We will investigate immediately
2. We will notify affected users within 72 hours
3. We will notify relevant authorities if required by law
4. We will take steps to prevent future breaches

---

