**How we use it:**
- Provide personalized predictions
- Show local weather and prices
- Improve app performance

**What we DON'T do:**
- ‚ùå Sell your data
- ‚ùå Track your location constantly
- ‚ùå Access your contacts/photos
- ‚ùå Share data with unauthorized parties

**Your control:**
- You can delete your account anytime
- You can disable analytics
- You can limit ad personalization
- You can deny location access

